meta.description: Clean and Customizable. Alternative to Just Enough Items/JEI.
meta.long_description: **(Snapshot versions of REI is on the Patreon)** _Clean and Customizable. An easy way to browse recipes._ #### Downloads contain files for Forge, Fabric and Rift! Please download the correct one! #### The Fabric version should be compatible on Quilt! --- Need a server to play with friends? Or don't know how to setup one? Just rent a server that is already configured! [](https://www.bisecthosting.com/shedaniel/) Click on the picture above, select plan, use my code **shedaniel** to get **25% off** your first month and enjoy playing with your friends! --- ## Recipes Exporting REI provides a keybind that is unbound by default that can be used to export recipes, here is an example: ## JEI Plugins Support: (Forge) This **DOES** support JEI plugins. Some mods might require REI Compatibility Workaround. If you wish to support both JEI and REI users on a server, install JEI alongside with REI Server Component on the server. ## Favourites / Bookmarking: Favouriting items are possible by pressing __A__ when hovering any items. ## Advanced Search: Mod: `@modname` Non-case sensitive, searching via mod, for example @materialisation to search for items added by materialisation. Tooltip: `#text` Non-case sensitive, searching via tooltip, for example #protection to search for protection books. Tags: `$tag` Non-case sensitive, searching via tags, for example $logs to search for logs. Regex: `r/regex/` Case sensitive, searching via regex, for example r/(Golden )?Apple) to search for golden apples or apples. Quotes: `"` Allowing spaces, for example "#protection iii" to search with spaces. Or: `|` Or, for example apple|$logs to search for apples or logs. ## Version Roadmap: REI 5 - Fabric 1.16.x - Bug Fixes until 28 Feb 2022 REI 6 - Forge 1.16.x - Feature Updates until Mar 2022 - Fabric 1.17.x - Feature Updates until Mar 2022 - Forge 1.17.x - Feature Updates until Mar 2022 REI 7 - Fabric 1.18 - Feature Updates until June 2022 - Forge 1.18 - Feature Updates until June 2022 REI 8 - Fabric 1.18.2 - Feature Updates until 1.20 (at least) - Forge 1.18.2 - Feature Updates until 1.20 (at least) REI 9 - Fabric 1.19 - Feature Updates until 1.20 (at least) - Forge 1.19 - Feature Updates until 1.20 (at least)
